Package jot.math

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Distance
    Abstract class that specifies the distance function to use.
    GJK
    Class that implements the Gilbert-Johnson-Keerthi algorithm for collision detection in 3D, as described in the video lecture at http://mollyrocket.com/849
    Interpolation
    Class that implements numerical interpolation algorithms.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Distance.DistanceType
    Available distance formulas: L1_NORM, L2_NORM, LINFINITY_NORM, and SQUARE.
